title: Celebrity Gossip Part 2 - Beyoncé Fires Back
description: In a rare move, Beyonce spoke out against the artists accusing her of using their music without permission. Plus, Kanye’s latest social media rants have gone too far, that both Instagram and Twitter stepped in.
